    getZoneOffset(android.health.connect.datatypes.AggregationType<T> aggregationType)
  class HealthConnectManager
    <T> aggregate(android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsRequest<T> request, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsResponse<T>,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
    <T> aggregateGroupByDuration(android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsRequest<T> request, java.time.Duration duration, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<java.util.List<android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsGroupedByDurationResponse<T>>,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
    <T> aggregateGroupByPeriod(android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsRequest<T> request, java.time.Period period, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<java.util.List<android.health.connect.AggregateRecordsGroupedByPeriodResponse<T>>,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
    deleteRecords(java.lang.Class<? extends android.health.connect.datatypes.Record> recordType, android.health.connect.TimeRangeFilter timeRangeFilter, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<java.lang.Void,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
    deleteRecords(java.util.List<android.health.connect.RecordIdFilter> recordIds, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<java.lang.Void,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
    getChangeLogs(android.health.connect.changelog.ChangeLogsRequest changeLogsRequest, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<android.health.connect.changelog.ChangeLogsResponse,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)

    updateRecords(java.util.List<android.health.connect.datatypes.Record> records, java.util.concurrent.Executor executor, android.os.OutcomeReceiver<java.lang.Void,android.health.connect.HealthConnectException> callback)
